<h2>Google Business Profile: Your Most Important Asset</h2>
<p>Your <a href="/blog/optimize-google-business-profile/">Google Business Profile</a> (GBP) is the single most important ranking factor for local cleaning searches. GBP signals account for 32% of <a href="/glossary/local-ranking-factors/">local ranking factors</a>. Your profile appears in the local pack, Google Maps, and AI Overviews before your website ever does.</p>
<h3>Set Up Your Profile Correctly</h3>
<p>Choose "House Cleaning Service" or "Commercial Cleaning Service" as your primary category. Add secondary categories that match your services:</p>
<ul>
<li>Carpet Cleaning Service</li>
<li>Window Cleaning Service</li>
<li>Janitorial Service</li>
<li>Maid Service</li>
<li>Office Cleaning Service</li>
</ul>
<h3>Complete Every Field</h3>
<p>Incomplete profiles lose to complete ones. Fill in every section:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Business name:</strong> Your exact legal name. Do not add keywords. "Sparkle Clean" is correct. "Sparkle Clean Best House Cleaning Austin TX" gets suspended.</li>
<li><strong>Service areas:</strong> List every city and zip code you serve. Google uses this data for "near me" searches.</li>
<li><strong>Phone number:</strong> Use a local number. It builds more trust than a toll-free number.</li>
<li><strong>Business hours:</strong> Keep these accurate. Update for holidays.</li>
<li><strong>Business description:</strong> 750 characters. Mention your city, services, and experience naturally.</li>
<li><strong>Services:</strong> Add each cleaning service individually with a brief description and price range.</li>
<li><strong>Photos:</strong> Upload 15+ photos. Before-and-after shots, team photos, branded vehicles, and equipment. Businesses with photos get 42% more requests for directions.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Post to GBP Regularly</h3>
<p>Post 2 to 3 times per week. Share cleaning tips, seasonal offers, before-and-after photos, and customer testimonials. Regular posting signals to Google that your business is active. For a complete strategy, see our <a href="/blog/gbp-posting-frequency/">GBP posting frequency guide</a>.</p>
<h3>Respond to Every Review</h3>
<p>Response rate matters for rankings. Reply to every review within 24 hours. Thank positive reviewers. Address negative reviews professionally. Use our <a href="/tools/review-response-generator/">review response generator</a> to save time while maintaining a personal tone.</p>
