<h3>Why Blogging Works for Cleaning Businesses</h3>
<p>A homeowner searching "how much does deep cleaning cost" today becomes a customer searching "deep cleaning service near me" next month. Blog content captures these early-stage researchers and positions your company as the obvious choice when they are ready to book.</p>
<p>Every blog post also:</p>
<ul>
<li>Creates a new indexed page targeting a specific keyword</li>
<li>Builds internal links to your service pages (boosting their rankings)</li>
<li>Demonstrates <a href="/glossary/e-e-a-t/">E-E-A-T</a> signals to Google</li>
<li>Provides content for GBP posts and social media</li>
