<ul>
<li><strong>Cost guides</strong> ("How Much Does House Cleaning Cost in [State]?"). Referenced by real estate and moving blogs</li>
<li><strong>Checklists</strong> ("The Ultimate Deep Cleaning Checklist"). Shared widely on Pinterest and social media</li>
<li><strong>Seasonal guides</strong> ("Spring Cleaning Guide for [City] Homes"). Picked up by local news and lifestyle sites</li>
